name: historic-air-photo-cd-rom-image-locator-for-idaho
notes: This application provides a way to geospatially locate a selected set of non-georeferenced scanned historic air photos for Idaho contained in the Idaho aerial views database. It allows users to determine the flight year, the University of Idaho CD-ROM call number, and the TIFF image name for every fifth image along a given project flight line. The selected projects contained include: 1927 Vertical air photos of the western portion of the Nez Perce National Forest 1928 Vertical air photos of the western portion of the Nez Perce National Forest 1929 Clearwater resource project: vertical air photos of the St. Joe & Clearwater National Forest, Idaho. 1932 Project N and C: vertical air photos of the Nez Perce and Clearwater National Forest Van Buren Creek, Riggins Hot Springs, Tollgate Creek, Cabin Creek, and Woodrat Mountain. Vertical air photos of the Selway National Forest, 1932 Fish Creek, Coolwater Ridge, Selway River, Fenn, and Lower Lochsa River, Idaho. 1933 Project S vertical air photos of Selway National Forest & northern Nez Perce National Forest, Idaho. Project JO air photos of eastern Latah and western Clearwater Counties, Idaho. Project J air photos, 1933 Latah County, Idaho. Project J and JO: air photos of the St. Joe National Forest. 1935 Project N, vertical air photos of the Eastern Nez Perce National Forest Meadow Creek, Bargamin Creek, Running Creek and the Selway River. 1936 Project EZ, vertical airphotos of the Eastern portion of the Cearwater National Forests. Project EV: vertical air photos of the Central and Eastern portions of the Nez Perce National Forest Elk City, Meadow Creek, Green Mountain, and Black Hawk Mountain. Project N, 1936 vertical air photos of the Nez Perce National Forest: Meadow Creek and the American River. 1937 Project CF 1937 vertical air photos of the Coeur d'Alene National Forest and vicinity (Kootenai County and Shoshone County. Project EZ: air photos of the Powell Ranger District of the Clearwater National Forest, Idaho. Project FA: air photos of the Powell Ranger District of the Clearwater National Forest, Idaho. 1939 Project FA and GSK: air photos of the Nez Perce National Forest Meadow Creek, Selway River and the western portion of the forest. 1948 Project C, 1948 air photos of the Clearwater National Forest, Idaho (Musselshell, Austin Ridge, Hemlock Butte, Lolo Creek, and Beaver Dam Saddle).
